sessions.session_desc:
iRacing Hillclimb Community: https://discord.gg/EETNAPCB8w 
 MX5 Deep Dive Community: https://discord.gg/hj274TyAmz 
 - 
 🥇 1st Place: $15 iRacing Credits 
 🥈 2nd Place: $10 iRacing Credits 
 🥉 3rd Place: $5 iRacing Credits 
 
 iRacing Hillclimb Community, in collaboration with the MX5 Deep Dive community, presents its first special event of the calendar year with the 2026 edition of "The First Hillclimb of the Year"! :Confetti: 
 
 "The First Hillclimb of the Year" is an iRacing hillclimb competition featuring the Global Mazda MX-5 Cup car on the hillclimb configuration of Mount Washington! Kick off the new year by enjoying the sights of New Hampshire as you battle against the clock in this 24 hour hosted server, with the top 3 on the leaderboard earning prizes of iRacing credits! 
 
 With static time, track, and weather conditions, the environment on the mountain will remain the same through the full 24 hours to guarantee competitive fairness throughout.

sessions.session_desc: "The Greatest Show on Virtual Dirt" takes it to the next level with this qualifying series. The most ambitious dirt drivers now have the opportunity to take their dirt-slinging skills to the Pro level by competing in this qualifying series. Drivers will take their 410 Sprint Cars and Super Late Models to many of the top dirt tracks on the iRacing service, and the ones that come out on top will be granted an elusive spot on the Pro grid!

sessions.session_desc: iRacing's regional series options for our racers around the world continue to expand with the creation of the iRacing GT3 Regional Tour. Each region features a diverse selection of tracks that are local and relevant to each region’s geography. While all iRacers are eligible to run in any region’s event, the servers will always be set to the most appropriate iRacing server for each region.
